/* 

	VJ Experiments
	
	Originally written to explore some systems to react to music or to dancers for a performance.
	Written in Open Frameworks 0071.
*/

Community addons required:

ofxTweenzor
ofxSyphon
ofxUI
ofxKinect

/*
	Apps
*/
FFT_UI - sends average FFT data over OSC
mouseOscController - mouse osc signals
ofxKinectPointCloud - working with point cloud data, saturation, and camera movement
openNI_NetworkController - sends cursor data over OSC and potentially other data
VJ_DisplayApp - using a simple GLSL shader , listens to openNI_NetworkController, current still does it's own FFT
